-- Essar Oil of India Is Seeking Exploration Assets in Africa, Times Reports
-- B y   R a k t e e m   K a t a k e y
-- 2010-10-21T00:42:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-21/essar-oil-is-seeking-exploration-assets-in-africa-economic-times-reports.html
Essar Oil Ltd. is close to buying
oil and gas exploration assets in Africa to feed its refineries,
Economic Times reported, citing Managing Director Naresh Nayyar.  Essar has identified at least six blocks in countries
including Nigeria, Libya and Madagascar, according to the
report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
